articles.title: Former ‘Kiddy Kapers’ TV star died when California wildfires ripped through Malibu estate, mother says - CNN
articles.description: A former child star from Australia died when the Los Angeles wildfires ripped through his family’s Malibu estate in California earlier this week, according to his mother.
